To Program to ESP8266 through arduino sketch
  follow instructions from 
  http://www.whatimade.today/esp8266-easiest-way-to-program-so-far/

When Programming 
  connect GPIO0 to gnd, powercycle esp, then program
  might have to try a few times until it works
  then you need to reset the device, and switch GPIO0 back to VDD
  
To monitor Serial Port go to serial monitor in sketch
Baud rate 115200, new line and cr

